
install lapack and blas

sudo apt-get install libblas-dev checkinstall
sudo apt-get install liblapacke-dev checkinstall

get git or:

git clone https://github.com/ITensor/ITensor itensor

install compiler gcc, g++

sudo cp options.mk.sample options.mk
chmod u+w ~/options.mk

sudo mcedit options.mk

comment macos system
uncomment llapack for linux system

in makefile, give path for itensor\ where the this.dir file lies



